---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../config";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ"
  description="About Aqwddda, the research interests behind this blog, and common questions."
>
  <h1 class="page-heading">FAQ / About</h1>
  <p class="page-intro">
    Background, research interests, and the purpose of this long-term technical notebook.
  </p>

  <div class="about-content">
    <section>
      <h2>Who writes this blog?</h2>
      <p>
        I am Aqwddda. I use this site to turn experiments, implementation notes, and
        reading into durable technical records.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What are the main research interests?</h2>
      <p>
        This blog focuses on recommendation systems, RAG, search, information retrieval,
        evaluation, and practical AI engineering.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How can I get in touch?</h2>
      <p>
        The public contact point is
        <a href={siteConfig.githubProfileUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          GitHub
        </a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Are posts final?</h2>
      <p>
        No. Articles may be revised when new evidence, implementation experience, or
        clearer explanations become available.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Can I reuse the code?</h2>
      <p>
        Check the repository license and the context around each example before reuse.
        Small snippets are educational examples and may omit production concerns.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content section {
    padding: 1.35rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
